    {
      "id": "PopularPost336540",
      "post_content": "Before the errata, this card was practically a white [Timewalk](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Timewalk) that was unrestricted. All it gave your opponent during their turn most of the time was an attack phase (if they even had creatures in play) and a draw (which was somewhat offset by the fact that this is a cantrip). It was sooooo broken. How it came to be printed with that wording, I will never know. ",
